`scenarioResultToBundle()` throws `BundleIntegrityError(code: 'no_initial_snapshot')`. Replayable scenario bundles 
require BOTH `captureInitialSnapshot: true` (the default) AND `captureCommandPayloads: true` on the scenario's history 
